Quote: A significant part of our problem is the deliberate PC use of the term "students" to give children an inflated idea of their own importance and standing... School children are not students. They are pupils, attending classes in an orderly fashion to be taught things. They will become students only when they leave the school system and go on to study at the university or some other institution.
